data.description: Discover the potential in this 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home, ideally located near Lackland AFB, Millers Pond Park, and Pearsall Park. Perfect for customizing to your liking or seizing as a rental opportunity, this residence opens up a world of possibilities. Whether you're looking to create your dream home or invest next to a key military base, this property offers an excellent foundation. Don't miss the chance to transform this house into a space that truly reflects your style or to capitalize on its strategic location for rental income. Explore the potential today and start imagining the future you can build here. New HVAC in 2022 and New Composition Shingle Roofing in 2023.
